claim.claim-text:
9. A method of selecting a control bit combination, comprising: 
determining a minimum value and a maximum value for a range of resistance values for a plurality of legal control bit combinations; 
selecting a desired resistance value within the range between the determined minimum value and the determined maximum value; 
approximating a resistance value for a control bit combination from the plurality of legal control bit combinations; and 
selecting the control bit combination based on a comparison between the approximated resistance value and the desired resistance value.

12. A method of selecting a control bit combination, comprising: 
determining a minimum value and a maximum value for a range of resistance values for a plurality of legal control bit combinations; 
approximating a minimum resistance value and a maximum resistance value of a control bit combination from the plurality of legal control bit combinations for a plurality of fabrication variations; 
selecting a desired resistance value within the range between the approximated minimum resistance value and the approximated maximum resistance value; and 
selecting the control bit combination based on the approximated minimum resistance value, the approximated maximum resistance value and the desired resistance value.
